commit.message:
re PR testsuite/51524 ([BMI2] New regression on 182266 vs 182257)

	PR testsuite/51524
	* gcc.target/i386/bmi2-mulx32-1.c (gen_mulx): Add attribute regparm(2).
	* gcc.target/i386/bmi2-mulx32-2.c (calc_mulx_u32): Ditto.

From-SVN: r182287
